anagram - Two strings having same length, same characters with the same frequencies.
output : True

1: Sort the strings

solution:
def is_anagram(s, t):
    return sorted(s) == sorted(t)

print(is_anagram("listen", "silent"))  

2: Using a frequency dictionary

solutions:
from collections import Counter

def is_anagram(s, t):
    return Counter(s) == Counter(t)

print(is_anagram("listen", "silent"))


Time Complexity :
Sorting approach: O(n log n)
Frequency counting approach: O(n)
